## Overview
Update `docs/PRODUCT_PLAN.md` to include the new Phase 6: Data Strategy & Intelligence, which extends the roadmap from v1.0 through v1.1.0.

## What Changed
Our brainstorming identified a critical strategic gap: Plaid has direct API connections to banks, while Plaidify currently only supports browser automation. Phase 6 addresses this by making Plaidify a **universal data access layer** that intelligently routes to the best data source.

